{"id":13806,"date":"2022-09-19T14:41:41","date_gmt":"2022-09-19T07:41:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/?p=13806"},"modified":"2022-09-24T14:43:08","modified_gmt":"2022-09-24T07:43:08","slug":"danh-gia-hyundai-creta-muot-ma-an-toan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/danh-gia-hyundai-creta-muot-ma-an-toan\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"article__sapo cms-desc\">Mang phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf g\u00f3c c\u1ea1nh, \u0111a d\u1ea1ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, Hyundai Creta l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac. C\u00f3 3.851 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Creta ch\u1ec9 sau 4 th\u00e1ng ra m\u1eaft t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/div>\n<div class=\"article__body cms-body\">\n<p>Hyundai Creta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 g\u00f3c c\u1ea1nh, c\u00e1 t\u00ednh r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 \u1edf c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf g\u1ed3m nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t kho\u00e1t. N\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn nghi\u00eang v\u00e0 ch\u00e9o xe, d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t g\u1ed3 gh\u1ec1, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1ea3n nhi\u1ec7t k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u h\u00ecnh thang, \u0111en b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb ban ng\u00e0y n\u1eb1m \u1ea9n khi t\u1eaft m\u00e1y. M\u1ed9t phong c\u00e1ch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 Parametric Hidden Jewelry nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em Tucson.<\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta-8567.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n\" data-index=\"0\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta-8567.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n \u1ea3nh 1\" data-image-id=\"3286698\" data-width=\"3000\" data-height=\"2002\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta-8567.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>\u1ede ph\u00eda th\u00e2n xe, Hyundai Creta ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi d\u00e1ng h\u00ecnh c\u01a1 b\u1eafp, kho\u1ebb kho\u1eafn. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec9nh tr\u1ee5 A, m\u1ed9t d\u1ea3i chrome vu\u1ed1t d\u00e0i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i tr\u1ee5 C g\u00e2y s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd. Ch\u1ea1y d\u1ecdc th\u00e2n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1eadp n\u1ed5i g\u00e2n gu\u1ed1c. Tay n\u1eafm c\u1eeda m\u1ea1 chrome. Ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a xe r\u1ea5t gi\u1ed1ng Hyundai Tucson, c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c copy t\u1eeb m\u1eabu xe \u0111\u00e0n anh sang. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 copy kh\u00e9o l\u00e9o, r\u1ea5t v\u1eeba v\u1eb7n v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc D\u00e0i x R\u1ed9ng x Cao l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 4.315 x 1.790 x 1.660 (mm) c\u00f9ng kho\u1ea3ng s\u00e1ng g\u1ea7m cao 200mm.<\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-6-of-24-2991.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n\" data-index=\"1\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-6-of-24-2991.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n \u1ea3nh 2\" data-image-id=\"3286707\" data-width=\"3000\" data-height=\"2002\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-6-of-24-2991.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Hyundai c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean t\u00f4 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho chi\u1ebfc SUV c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi n\u00f3c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u01a1n \u0111en, n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u00e0 tr\u1ebb trung \u1edf b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p, lazang xe l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i h\u1ee3p kim nh\u00f4m m\u1eb7t c\u1eaft kim c\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng k\u00ednh 17 inch, t\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh c\u00e1nh qu\u1ea1t c\u1ed1i xay gi\u00f3. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean h\u00ecnh d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc SUV c\u1ee1 nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00ed ch\u1ea5t \u201c\u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng\u201d.<\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-10-of-24-6939.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n\" data-index=\"2\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-10-of-24-6939.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n \u1ea3nh 3\" data-image-id=\"3286704\" data-width=\"3000\" data-height=\"2002\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-10-of-24-6939.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n \u0111u\u00f4i xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e8n h\u1eadu d\u1ea1ng LED \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u1ea1 m\u1eaft. K\u1ebb khen ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u00ea, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u00e2n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfc xe. Ph\u1ea7n g\u00f3c tho\u00e1t sau l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 32 \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u00fap t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 xe tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00e0 g\u00e2n gu\u1ed1c, m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-22-of-24-1228.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n\" data-index=\"3\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-22-of-24-1228.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n \u1ea3nh 4\" data-image-id=\"3286699\" data-width=\"3000\" data-height=\"2002\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-22-of-24-1228.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Tuy v\u1eady, Creta l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc SUV \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y trong \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb cao h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111i r\u1eebng, \u0111i n\u00fai. Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 7 n\u0103m khi c\u00f3 2 trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 x\u0103ng v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u 1.6L, l\u1ea7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Creta ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 trang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 SmartStream c\u00f3 dung t\u00edch 1.5L phun x\u0103ng \u0111a \u0111i\u1ec3m. Kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 n\u00e0y cho c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 115 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i 6.300 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat c\u00f9ng Momen xo\u1eafn 144 Nm t\u1ea1i 4.500 v\u00f2ng\/ph\u00fat. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 h\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 v\u00f4 c\u1ea5p iVT.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 k\u00e9m h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn nh\u01b0 kh\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 Turbo c\u1ee7a KIA Seltos hay Peugeot 2008. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u, v\u1edbi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng, Creta c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng.<\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai-creta-trip-2-7791.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n\" data-index=\"4\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai-creta-trip-2-7791.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n \u1ea3nh 5\" data-image-id=\"3286697\" data-width=\"3000\" data-height=\"1968\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai-creta-trip-2-7791.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>Khi \u1edf \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea3i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb, Creta t\u1ecf ra l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe kh\u00e1 \u201cngoan\u201d: c\u00e1ch \u00e2m t\u1ed1t, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb v\u1ecdng ti\u1ebfng m\u00e1y hay ti\u1ebfng xe c\u1ed9 di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o cabin d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u1ea5m m\u00fat ti\u00eau \u00e2m. V\u00f4 l\u0103ng tr\u1ee3 l\u1ef1c \u0111i\u1ec7n nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e1i kh\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. Khi di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cao t\u1ed1c v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ee3 l\u1ef1c gi\u1ea3m d\u1ea7n, khi\u1ebfn tay l\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7m h\u01a1n, r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 an to\u00e0n cho chi\u1ebfc xe c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i trong xe.<\/p>\n<p>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u00eau d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 y\u00ean t\u00e2m v\u1edbi Creta khi xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u201cv\u0169 trang\u201d h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec7n \u00edch an to\u00e0n: phanh ABS, c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed ESC, kh\u1edfi h\u00e0nh ngang d\u1ed1c HAC, ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t ch\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1ee3t th\u00e2n xe VSM, 6 t\u00fai kh\u00ed, th\u00e9p gia c\u01b0\u1eddng AHSS c\u00f9ng k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u khung xe Hive Structure d\u1ea1ng t\u1ed5 ong, c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh l\u00e0 \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng SmartSense v\u1edbi phanh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng FCA, c\u00f9ng gi\u1eef l\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, gi\u1eef v\u00f4 l\u0103ng, c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe \u0111\u00e0n anh, v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean Creta trong su\u1ed1t qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh di chuy\u1ec3n.<\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-14-of-24-690.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n\" data-index=\"5\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-14-of-24-690.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n \u1ea3nh 6\" data-image-id=\"3286701\" data-width=\"3000\" data-height=\"2002\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-14-of-24-690.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>V\u00ec l\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean khu v\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed3i n\u00fai M\u1ed9c Ch\u00e2u, S\u01a1n La v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00fac cua g\u1ea5p, m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1ed3 gh\u1ec1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1ed5 g\u00e0, chi\u1ebfc xe v\u1eabn v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. Hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1eb7n xo\u1eafn khung khi v\u00e0o cua \u1edf t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 b\u1ecb tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau h\u1ebft. C\u00e1c c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh l\u00e1i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e8n b\u00e1o ESC nh\u1ea5p nh\u00e1y ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng an to\u00e0n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u1ed7i khi ch\u00e2n ga h\u01a1i qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o cua h\u01a1i gi\u00e0.<\/p>\n<p>Do s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1p kh\u00e1 d\u1ea7y: 215\/60 n\u00ean xe ch\u1ea1y kh\u00e1 \u00eam d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb9p, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng g\u1ea7m cao 200mm khi\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c v\u01b0\u1ee3t \u1ed5 g\u00e0 tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. H\u1ed9p s\u1ed1 iVT v\u1edbi 1 b\u00e1nh r\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00f9ng d\u00e2y \u0111ai d\u1ea1ng x\u00edch gi\u00fap chi\u1ebfc xe v\u1ecdt \u0111i c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n, c\u1ea3m x\u00fac h\u01a1n sau m\u1ed7i c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p ga.<\/p>\n<p>Tuy v\u1eady, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t 115 m\u00e3 l\u1ef1c tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t th\u00e2n x\u00e1c xe 1,3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f9ng 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong xe, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc xe m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. \u1ede d\u1ea3i t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eeb 0 \u2013 80km\/h, Creta kh\u00e1 lanh l\u1eb9 v\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean 80 km\/h, xe t\u1ecf ra \u0111u\u1ed1i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n s\u1ee9c v\u1ecdt n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n leo \u0111\u00e8o v\u00e0 c\u00f3 cua, Creta kh\u00e1 \u0111u\u1ed1i v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i t\u00ednh to\u00e1n th\u1eadt k\u0129 nh\u1eefng c\u00fa v\u01b0\u1ee3t. S\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu l\u1eaby chuy\u1ec3n s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean v\u00f4 l\u0103ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i k\u00e9m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n \u1edf nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 tay gi\u1ea3 l\u1eadp \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng th\u00eam Momen xo\u1eafn.<\/p>\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Creta kh\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7: m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u1ee9ng trung t\u00e2m 10.25 inch s\u1eafc n\u00e9t, h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i th\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng Android Auto\/Apple Carplay, 8 loa Bose c\u00f9ng ampli r\u1eddi cho ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u00e2m thanh gi\u1ea3i tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac. Gh\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i b\u1ecdc da to\u00e0n b\u1ed9, c\u00f3 trang b\u1ecb l\u00e0m m\u00e1t gh\u1ebf , c\u1eeda gi\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau k\u00e8m s\u1ea1c \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i USB ti\u1ec7n \u00edch. Xe trang b\u1ecb phanh tay \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed, gi\u1eef phanh Autohold, r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n trong vi\u1ec7c di chuy\u1ec3n trong \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<table class=\"picture\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"pic\"><a class=\"photo\" href=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w1000\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-12-of-24-1491.jpg\" data-desc=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n\" data-index=\"6\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"cms-photo lazyloaded\" src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-12-of-24-1491.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Hyundai Creta: M\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, an to\u00e0n \u1ea3nh 7\" data-image-id=\"3286693\" data-width=\"3000\" data-height=\"2002\" data-photo-original-src=\"\" data-src=\"https:\/\/photo-cms-tpo.zadn.vn\/w645\/Uploaded\/2022\/fmivbziv\/2022_08_24\/ban-sao-cua-hyundai---creta---ori-12-of-24-1491.jpg\" \/><\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 730 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng cho phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n cao c\u1ea5p, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec7n nghi v\u1ec1 trang b\u1ecb v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 d\u00f9ng trong v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh. Hyundai Creta mang \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh tin c\u1eady, v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0 v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ec7n gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n di chuy\u1ec3n an to\u00e0n. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n gi\u1eefa v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 670 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u1ee3p l\u00ed h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh hay mong mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u1ee9c ti\u1ec1n h\u01a1n 700 tri\u1ec7u.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Mang phong c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf g\u00f3c c\u1ea1nh, \u0111a d\u1ea1ng t\u00ednh n\u0103ng an to\u00e0n c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh m\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u00e0, Hyundai Creta l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc xe c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng trong ph\u00e2n kh\u00fac. C\u00f3 3.851 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 doanh s\u1ed1 b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Creta ch\u1ec9 sau 4 th\u00e1ng [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":13267,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[1,30],"tags":[],"yst_prominent_words":[],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13806"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=13806"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13806\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":13807,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/13806\/revisions\/13807"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/13267"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=13806"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=13806"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=13806"},{"taxonomy":"yst_prominent_words","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/hyundaihaiphong.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/yst_prominent_words?post=13806"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}